* Carnage snarled deeply, she didn't care to her this clone talk about her 
dead friend like that! How dare she even speak his name with such 
carelessness!
Carnage stopped and waited for the clone to walk ahead then brought her jaws 
down on the tip of it's tail, it was just a quick snap...just enough to draw 
mech fluid and hurt just enough for the clone to get her  point.If Cyber 
Claw was going to travel with them then she had to get one thing straight!*

" You shut your trap! If I ever..ever hear you speak about my friend like 
that again I'll tear you limb from  limb! You understand me? Weather you 
think I can do it or not! So if you want to travel with my friend and I it 
would advise that you drop this ' I can do anything since I look like 
Dinobot' slag!"

* Carnage then walked up beside Cyber Claw and looked at her through the 
side of her eye, then turned her attention to the road ahead.
This clone was pushing her luck!*
